    ROZ  Romania, East Europe.
    RUZ  Russia, East Europe.
    PLZ  Poland, East Europe.
    BGZ  Bulgaria, East Europe.
    CZZ  Czech Republic, East Europe.
    SKZ  Slovakia, East Europe.
</CN>
